headline.main: Investors Bet Trump-Fueled Tech Rally Far From Over
headline.print_headline: Investors Bet Trump-Fueled Tech Rally Far From Over

lead_paragraph: (Reuters)or - Rory McIlroy proved better at holing out from the fairway than making short putts on his way to a two-stroke lead after the second round at the WGC-Mexico Championship in Mexico City on Friday.
